traineddata: Discord is a Chat platform where users can create, join, chat, and make new friends. They are able to join servers, create servers for communities, and much more!
Roblox is an online gaming platform for people to play, create games and much more!
The Roblox friends limit is 200 Friends.
Roblox is slowly increasing the maximum friends limit from 200, to 1000 which will be in full affect in early to late 2025.
